snippet.title: This is the Prove that Amber Heard is Lying | Flixet
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to share something which will prove that amber heard is lying. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_______________________________________________________

Johnny Depp's defamation case against a British tabloid who accused him of assaulting his ex-wife Amber Heard ended in a London court on Tuesday, July 28, when the star's lawyer called Heard a "compulsive liar" and claimed that Depp was the real victim of abuse in the relationship.
